e789c32bb89d9f840ee3264a9b9bae8fbd7c3b6","tid":528400,"uid":629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>7年前洗左5萬幾做下鼻甲微創手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果比我簡多次我一定唔會做，依d慢性鼻病睇中醫先係正途</blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有後遺症？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:38:47.000Z","msg":"1係治標不治本 因為慢性鼻病既本質係因為你既五臟六腑出問題而通過鼻部發作出黎，所以用手術/西藥/噴鼻黎醫治的話好多時只係短期有效，一停用或者冇幾耐之後就會返發，因為問題既重點根本唔係鼻度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2係空鼻症問題，有興趣可以google睇下"},{"pid":"fe18cba7cc7296e69d99223860f978369b675c38","tid":528400,"uid":99302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:45:29.000Z","msg":"睇專科話我鼻骨咩埋一邊，但我唔敢磨鼻骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a024eb76d27ff72287391e2cd4c92f98b0a6af1","tid":528400,"uid":20134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:54:16.000Z","msg":"想睇下你地割完成效會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我十至廿年鼻敏感用中醫方法清乾淨曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無服用任何中藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff8b05aa4c7dd55fb29e5fc9da5fc5a4c2dc603","tid":528400,"uid":155654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d98945f2c284daef3d07d8fbb5ed24f6762218ee","tid":528400,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T17:22:04.000Z","msg":"岩岩用電筒照下個鼻<br />\n下鼻甲腫撚到仆街 <br />\n搞到個鼻塞撚哂<br />\nd鼻涕又呻唔到出黎 搞到倒流<br />\n引致喉嚨長期多痰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用口呼吸 朝朝個喉嚨乾到仆街<br />\n有無巴打試過割 係咪好快又打回原形？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:54:43.000Z","msg":"鼻下甲 　+ 鼻中隔成形 + 切埋扁桃腺  6萬無反彈"},{"pid":"d28cb19b6f175f583fc3e00a523275d4ca72861b","tid":528400,"uid":20134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:55:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想睇下你地割完成效會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我十至廿年鼻敏感用中醫方法清乾淨曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無服用任何中藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細個鼻竇炎嚴重到老母帶我睇西醫<br />\n狂噴狂食啲收鼻水既藥都沒用"},{"pid":"9892088744dfd012e14c20085d3a0567cf3448ba","tid":528400,"uid":155654,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:57:11.000Z","msg":"之前塞到心跳加速 好彩有保險"},{"pid":"ce7e536c356b72ad1e66b65230b31da73e6b0f6f","tid":528400,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a024eb76d27ff72287391e2cd4c92f98b0a6af1","tid":528400,"uid":20134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:54:16.000Z","msg":"想睇下你地割完成效會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我十至廿年鼻敏感用中醫方法清乾淨曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無服用任何中藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:04:40.000Z","msg":"用咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f56c963a3154779414c94a053f49d1a37bc7596","tid":528400,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:06:10.000Z","msg":"究竟幾時先會有一食就醫好敏感既藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a6f65c7cb4725fd92284e066ad610f7cf824ed","tid":528400,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:07:21.000Z","msg":"我有幾粒大既鼻息肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3b56cc3ad37624815f5359f1446d2dc8b47644","tid":528400,"uid":118924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:15:43.000Z","msg":"值得一割，上年7月割左，舒服好多。係侵會割，護士好溫柔"},{"pid":"a5dd7657ab91f7ecb3e3e318b8c85881c04cc633","tid":528400,"uid":20134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:19:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想睇下你地割完成效會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我十至廿年鼻敏感用中醫方法清乾淨曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無服用任何中藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>用咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nkeep住每日艾炙一兩個穴位半個鐘，持續左幾個星期<br />\n不過唔好聽我講完就走去買艾條亂咁燒自己<br />\n唔一定work,只係我個病因乎合,進行治療先咁順利。<br />\n詳細就請教下你信得過既中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔鼓勵亂咁試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw我都是讀中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f3c14d3f930fe04801b74dad706a802dc4de07","tid":528400,"uid":52369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:25:03.000Z","msg":"公立做 訓一晚出院 手勢幾好 係抽出黎果陣差少少暈"},{"pid":"8e8dd150db1c66140e8b290873f2456489bea0e5","tid":528400,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"265182aefc31025266ff9f45970aa31335b954c8","tid":528400,"uid":118719,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T09:22:35.000Z","msg":"7年前洗左5萬幾做下鼻甲微創手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果比我簡多次我一定唔會做，依d慢性鼻病睇中醫先係正途"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:51:22.000Z","msg":"唔會做既原因係？"},{"pid":"3f6ede50d62c64d9320e560976cada85f3f9eeec","tid":528400,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7f3c14d3f930fe04801