" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:18:11.000Z","msg":"我果個醫生其實個人幾好 <br />\n但我都好認同佢係好用力地扯出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一扯出黎果下成盤係血 仲多過成個經期的血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都流左個幾鐘<br />\n<br />\n我好似是手術後兩天才抆 未抆果時一邊眼狂標眼水<br />\n食野飲野吞果下 會好似浸親咁 （好難形容）<br />\n本身帶左部ipad入去煲劇 但完全無心機去睇 同打機"},{"pid":"542a1bc396c12987cfdc777362cbf1954c46cd17","tid":528400,"uid":73787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a934176b00c1d2f04c9d34e090e72da6fab4eb8","tid":528400,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27f79017197f7a239338c49c126a82f88c541473","tid":528400,"uid":159183,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"95ed9bb7014dbff8a933ce2cfb15d40cd8f720dc","tid":528400,"uid":76370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T01:09:34.000Z","msg":"有無試過洗鼻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T01:20:47.000Z","msg":"點樣洗？ <br />\n有無產品可以洗鼻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:50:23.000Z","msg":"生理鹽水 自己google啦仆街<br />\n成本唔使30蚊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:20:04.000Z","msg":"其實同洗傷口果種 一包包 粉紅色 果隻有唔同<br />\n果時我做完手術以為是用果隻 <br />\n一個星期後返去覆診<br />\n醫生叫我唔好用果隻<br />\n佢話 用食鹽 和暖水 撈埋就可以"},{"pid":"1268698f92d141667a00d3d28de27ee1a3314650","tid":528400,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da481fb627bc9c6acc03462f62288b7d23e92073","tid":528400,"uid":52369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f6ede50d62c64d9320e560976cada85f3f9eeec","tid":528400,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7f3c14d3f930fe04801b74dad706a802dc4de07","tid":528400,"uid":52369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:25:03.000Z","msg":"公立做 訓一晚出院 手勢幾好 係抽出黎果陣差少少暈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:52:17.000Z","msg":"公立做要排幾多年？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:12:52.000Z","msg":"半"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:21:18.000Z","msg":"咁快？<br />\n<br />\n點排期？ 第一步去睇門診 ？"},{"pid":"bf12bc546208289ea73a77b26bf6e95668aaadca","tid":528400,"uid":73787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2aa298410a38c832b03e49fe78b75ddb5609654","tid":528400,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f740358b590f61898378234af97ab26e10cd0dc1","tid":528400,"uid":44403,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"dfbf918552be1b71225741a704eee932ba8bd39e","tid":528400,"uid":73787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T01:18:19.000Z","msg":"割左四個月 無生返出黎的情況<br />\n<br />\n你不如睇睇醫生會唔會有埋鼻中隔問題？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T01:29:49.000Z","msg":"一樣，本身鼻塞左廿幾年，用口抖氣，成日好易感冒同喉嚨乾到痛，半年前做左鼻中隔同下鼻甲手術，宜家通到仆街，發現原來兩邊鼻窿都有氣入係咁爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:50:54.000Z","msg":"醫生叫我做 <br />\n上網睇過<br />\n好驚個鼻會塌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:21:23.000Z","msg":"我是無扁左 但頭幾個月個鼻骨會有少少痛 同唔硬<br />\n要注意唔好比人掂個鼻"},{"pid":"aac6a25ab55c9ba19f5da65eaacc51a2f1d81416","tid":528400,"uid":73787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28290028f6e43956f089a06deca1e069d0394376","tid":528400,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfbf918552be1b71225741a704eee932ba8bd39e","tid":528400,"uid":73787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T01:18:19.000Z","msg":"割左四個月 無生返出黎的情況<br />\n<br />\n你不如睇睇醫生會唔會有埋鼻中隔問題？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:53:54.000Z","msg":"有冇邊位醫生好？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:21:39.000Z","msg":"我睇公立的"},{"pid":"9efe7c4a3c4025975da08fcfe4457452c5b23d3b","tid":528400,"uid":73787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da2e4473af272837003b4e9df0a3ac5b1f1d07a1","tid":528400,"uid":74177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T08:58:56.000Z","msg":"有無巴打做過鼻中隔個手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大概