>\n係唔會兩邊一齊通哂"},{"pid":"b92bd189fccf244119e39ac7295a6d9fab7b2062","tid":528400,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T16:24:38.000Z","msg":"我噴極都冇用 因為入面結構性問題"},{"pid":"0c04ddf7eb88323b424d81e415247f7d0c5d476c","tid":528400,"uid":44403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38a1c390156a136dafe2f7606e9df512dc40534a","tid":528400,"uid":73787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"115d2d72408cf797153dc8e2cca16bce5f355fd0","tid":528400,"uid":44403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1885baf64b9529f2386b5d681c6b72c3e4c74e03","tid":528400,"uid":73787,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T05:35:39.000Z","msg":"諗返起留院兩日 抆返兩條fu料出黎就...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:52:15.000Z","msg":"個時術後唔夠24小時條垃圾醫生就監粗抆我條敷料出黎想趕我出院，結果好似噴泉咁流左成個鐘血，止唔到血，成個鼻同口都係血，個下真係幾驚休克死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:18:11.000Z","msg":"我果個醫生其實個人幾好 <br />\n但我都好認同佢係好用力地扯出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一扯出黎果下成盤係血 仲多過成個經期的血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都流左個幾鐘<br />\n<br />\n我好似是手術後兩天才抆 未抆果時一邊眼狂標眼水<br />\n食野飲野吞果下 會好似浸親咁 （好難形容）<br />\n本身帶左部ipad入去煲劇 但完全無心機去睇 同打機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T23:16:10.000Z","msg":"同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64458c40051655b8dc50e4a626cb9a3def474b5c","tid":528400,"uid":52369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1268698f92d141667a00d3d28de27ee1a3314650","tid":528400,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da481fb627bc9c6acc03462f62288b7d23e92073","tid":528400,"uid":52369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f6ede50d62c64d9320e560976cada85f3f9eeec","tid":528400,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:52:17.000Z","msg":"公立做要排幾多年？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:12:52.000Z","msg":"半"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:21:18.000Z","msg":"咁快？<br />\n<br />\n點排期？ 第一步去睇門診 ？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:58:09.000Z","msg":"我兒科轉去睇"},{"pid":"61ab294d4506a5179f79e38ca4a83d0f7c787e70","tid":528400,"uid":862,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T19:40:54.000Z","msg":"點解仲有咁多人用安鼻x?<br />\n記得o個陣睇私家醫生話用呢d 標榜無類固既藥物 長期用會令鼻甲硬化 噴幾多藥都消唔到腫 佢叫我如果用噴霧要用有類固的<br />\n<br />\n我自己2年前就做私家 訓左2晚醫院 無記錯好似54000 不過自己公司保險差唔多cover 晒 我自己覺得應該做 因為我自己以前係一到夜晚 又或者進出冷氣地方就會鼻塞 有時噴霧都無用消唔到腫 夜晚要用口呼氣 朝早喉嚨又乾又痛<br />\n<br />\n但做左2年 誇張d講句 我未試過有一日鼻塞 好撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a355daf86a8f47c37c36eac427e79a783f7ebf","tid":528400,"uid":113074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T20:17:39.000Z","msg":"唔做就鼻塞 <br />\n做咗就空鼻症抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做手術只係治標<br />\n最好都係由環境方面著手"}]}